  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-02-10",
    "date": "2025-03-28T13:55:28Z",
    "text": "Recovery of Stolen Checks Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of the Treasury to establish procedures that allow an eligible taxpayer to elect to receive by direct deposit a replacement of a federal tax refund amount that was originally issued as a paper check and was lost or stolen. (Currently, taxpayers eligible to receive a replacement of a lost or stolen federal tax refund check are generally issued another paper check.)"
  },
